      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Multi Line Text Area Block</uicontrol>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The Multi Line Text Area block is very similar to Single Line Text block. It enables you to write long texts in multiple lines.<fig class="- topic/fig ">
